content.raw:
The `EXAMPLE_example_plugins` test is [timing out](http://build.osrfoundation.org/job/gazebo-any-sdformat-any-devel-trusty-amd64/22/testReport/%28root%29/EXAMPLE_example_plugins/test_ran/):

~~~
299: [==========] Running 11 tests from 1 test case.
299: [----------] Global test environment set-up.
299: [----------] 11 tests from ExamplePlugins/ExamplePlugins
299: [ RUN      ] ExamplePlugins/ExamplePlugins.Build/0
299/336 Test #299: EXAMPLE_example_plugins ...............................***Timeout 240.01 sec
~~~

I've confirmed on my desktop. It's weird. The gtest gets no console output. I see the `cmake` process, but it doesn't create much in the build folder.
